

<h1>Local Fruit Market </h1>
<div class="container d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center mt-4">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col mb-2">
      <%=image_tag image_path("home/peach-farm.jpg"), alt: "home", size: "370x230" %>
  
      <%=image_tag image_path("home/b-berry-farm.jpg"), alt: "home", size: "280x230" %>
      
      <%=image_tag image_path("home/mango-farm-1.jpg"), alt: "home", size: "300x230" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <%=image_tag image_path("home/strawberry-farm-1.jpg"), alt: "home", size: "300x230" %>
    
      <%=image_tag image_path("home/pear-farm.jpg"), alt: "home", size: "310x230" %>
    
      <%=image_tag image_path("home/dragon-farm.jpg"), alt: "home", size: "340x230" %>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="row season-intro d-flex flex-column justify-content-center mt-5 text-aligh-center" style="width:90%">
    <h3>Australian Local Fruits</h3>
    <p>Australia is a country that produces a wide variety of fruits. The land and the climate are diverse, allowing nummerious types of fruits to grow and ripen in all seasons. In winter time, the most abundant selections are lemons, mandarins, and oranges. </p>

    <span id="note">Check our seasonal fruits page to discover more guides >> </span>
    
  </div>

  <div class="row links d-flex justify-content-end mt-3" style="width:90%;" id="link-button">

    <%= link_to "seasonal fruits ", season_path, class: "btn btn-info mt-2 mr-2 mb-2" %>
    <%= link_to "see our products", products_path, class: "btn btn-info mt-2 mr-2 mb-2"%> 
      
   
  </div>
  
  <div class="row col-12 d-flex justify-content-start mt-3" style="width:90%;">
    <a id="contact-us" href="#contact-us"><h3>Contact Us</h3></a>
  </div>

    <div class="row mt-1" style="width:90%;">

      <div class="col-3 d-flex flex-column" id="contact-us-pic">
        <%=image_tag image_path("home/farmer-contact.jpg"), alt: "Us", size: "150x150" %>

        <button class="btn btn-success mb-5" style="width:150px; " type="submit">Submit</button>    
      </div>

    

      <div class="col-9 mb-5 mt-2">  

        <form action="https://formspree.io/mjvozkeg" method="POST">
      
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="name" name="name" id="name" placeholder="Enter your name" class="form-control">
          </div>

        
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter your email"  class="form-control">
          </div>
        

          <div class="form-group">
            <textarea class="form-control" name="comment" id="comment" placeholder="Enter your message" ></textarea>
          </div>
            
        </form>
      </div>  
      
  </div>
</div>
  